Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:06.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(280,280)\blur3}隣に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:11.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(280,280)\blur3}優しさあつめて　不思議みつけよう
