Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:53.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}便迎来大家沐浴阳光的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:58.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}亲如一家
