Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:06.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}相守相望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:11.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(280,280)\blur3}采撷点滴温馨 探索奇妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}天空近在咫尺
